<plot>This isn't just the Spice Girls first four video clips, it's a sort of film diary of their experiences over 1996-1997. There are loads of interviews, behind the scenes footage at video shoots, pillow fights, dances and general Spice Girl madness. You'll learn that the girls don't only talk about Girl Power.. they live it!</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?510205</url></doc>
